{"tid":1233732,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我唔會叫鄺仔做鄺神","createTime":"2019-06-16T20:52:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T05:28:38.000Z","uid":89476,"like":84,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d64fdac08df52654e2620c004b9c70a00c0fc372","tid":1233732,"uid":89476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T20:52:41.000Z","msg":"我欣賞佢 好幫得手 除左好幫到我地嘅需要 <br />\n仲幫手做左一個好嘅議員<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">榜樣</span></span><br />\n<br />\n但佢唔係神 佢係人<br />\n佢做嘅野 其他人一樣做到 其他議員一樣做到<br />\n我唔會立亂神化佢<br />\n我亦都唔會<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">倚賴</span></span>佢<br />\n<br />\n希望大家唔會隨便倚賴一個自己ff嘅英雄 而<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">鬆懈</span></span><br />\n<br />\n就算真係有一位英雄出現<br />\n希望大家都唔會忘記自己嘅本分<br />\n<br />\n香港係靠每個香港人自己救"},{"pid":"8610bdb7d62fce242a34e84fbf702daf3e20a92f","tid":1233732,"uid":89476,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T20:56:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">自己救</span></span>"},{"pid":"12aaf27a1d2e67cea4b9dc995361922cd8964eb1","tid":1233732,"uid":89476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T21:23:07.000Z","msg":"靠自己"},{"pid":"2d887a054cbe02e2d881b62b86e2afbaef2577b0","tid":1233732,"uid":91967,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T21:25:34.000Z","msg":"自己香港自己救。"},{"pid":"de9895aaddea0181b220782f6b733437f270e84e","tid":1233732,"uid":91967,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T21:28:18.000Z","msg":"同時，唔好鄺仔講咩就全盤接受，要經自己思考過濾。<br />\n<br />\n鄺仔唔係聖人，都會有判斷錯誤嘅時候。"},{"pid":"8a6d0be1068081aa9a6ce91cffd9f01a5089a217","tid":1233732,"uid":89476,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"de9895aaddea0181b220782f6b733437f270e84e","tid":1233732,"uid":91967,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T21:28:18.000Z","msg":"同時，唔好鄺仔講咩就全盤接受，要經自己思考過濾。<br />\n<br />\n鄺仔唔係聖人，都